name: Falling Away From Me - Korn
description:
The third piece of a small collection of AI-generated art based on bands, their music names, and/or lyrics.

"Falling Away From Me - Korn"  
Many of us have experienced moments where we feel like we've fallen out of touch with ourselves. 
We start viewing life from an outsider's perspective as if we've no control over our actions. 
Autopiloting through life a feeling of numbness sets in. 
Until a voice inside starts to be heard. 
First, it's only but a whisper but it rapidly evolves into loud cries. 
Cries of help.
A call to action!
Our conscience wants to regain control but we're too scared freefalling into the void... 
.
.
.
.
Until...
.

We hit the ground running!
We use that momentum to grow, jump back up stronger, more mature, and definitely wiser!
